text: A Trump Republican is a member of the Republican Party in the United States who supports the policies and beliefs of Donald Trump, the fourty fifth President of the United States. Trump Republicans tend to be some of the most conservative members of the Republican Party in not only the general public, but also in Congress, with the House of Representatives in particular having some of the most notable Trumpist Republicans (such as Matt Gaetz, Marjorie Taylor Greene, etc.).
